		parallel - build and execute shell command lines from standard input in parallel
		并行执行shell命令

$ sudo apt-get install parallel		


			parallel - build and execute shell command lines from standard input in parallel

$ cat *.csv | parallel  --pipe grep '13113'			


设置块大小

$ cat *.csv | parallel --block 10M --pipe grep '131136688'
